title: Riki Lindhome
description: Riki Lindhome (Garfunkel and Oates, Making It podcast) is one of Pete's favorite people and a wonderful YMIW guest: hilarious, thoughtful, and a nice sample of Pete just gabbin' like one of the gals. GABBIN' LIKE GALS was the original name of this podcast. JK. Enjoy, you weirdos!!
